<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Servant's Staff Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to Josper Kenshed in the Wizards' Guild in Erudin.  He will give you a bag to fill with Ice Goblin Beads.<BR>
<BR>
2) Head to Everfrost and kill Ice Goblin Casters to get the Ice Goblin Beads.  They drop rarely.  You will usually get shattered beads.<BR>
<BR>
3) Fill the bag with Ice Goblin Beads and then head back to Erudin and give the bag to Josper.  You will receive the Servant's Staff.</div>
<BR>
